      <title>SEC 批准交易所以半美分单位报价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/sec-poised-to-vote-on-overhaul-of-stock-pricing-exchange-fees</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国证券交易委员会已批准相关规则，允许交易所交易的数千只股票和 ETF 以半美分增量进行报价。]]></description>
